note:
I am a Data Consultant based in Western Australia.

I enjoy composing music and camping in the Australian Outback. I am a consumer of apple products with a variety of products including iMacs, MacBooks, iPads, iPhones, and Apple TVs in use in my family of 5.

I also capture images with my Fujifilm X-H2.

Though of Irish heritage, I identify as Australian, and I am a proud supporter of indigenous rights. I acknowledge Whadjuk Noongar people as the traditional custodians of the land.
